      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe. i need help defining the 'ideal consumer' profile so we can nail the brand alignment. can u give me a detailed breakdown of who this person is? like their lifestyle, what they value, and their typical cultural or ethnic background to help us target the right markets? thanks.",
