      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your ideal consumer is typically an established, ultra-high-net-worth individual (UHNWI) or a successful high-achiever, often in their 40s to 60s. Their lifestyle involves private aviation, exclusive memberships, and appreciation for bespoke craftsmanship over mere ostentation. They value heritage, enduring quality, and discreet exclusivity, often favoring understated luxury. While not defined by a single background, successful individuals in finance, established industry leadership, and global arts circles are primary targets.",
