    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start with the lifestyle stuff. but when we're talking about \"heritage\" and \"established industry leadership,\" it feels a bit vague for a marketing deck. if we're looking at the most traditional, core demographic that actually buys these pieces, what kind of ethnic or racial profile are we looking at? i want to make sure our imagery and casting for the campaign feel authentic to that \"old money\" aesthetic you mentioned.",
